    "created_at": "2014-12-10T19:58:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-12-10T19:58:13Z",
    "body": "Cross-compilation is not that easy. I didn't have a spare box to put a Linux distribution on, and if I did, there would have been a learning curve in getting the cross-compiler working for my target. On the other hand, rustc codegen should already generate mostly target-independent IR, right?\n",
