    "body": "@Thiez I'm not sure how stable features applies here. The compiler could easily use _new_ stable features that old compilers don't know about. However there should always exist (even today) a chain of compilers that you can compile to eventually migrate your build to master. It just might be hundreds of compilers long.\n",
